snippet.textDisplay: I remember the first time fighting this fella. All was going good until I saw Sif dragging his poor paws because his health was so low to the extent his moves was slagging. I swear, I felt freaking sad at this point and as I killed him I was like...."Was this...worth it? Was killing a wolf who guarded his best friend worth killing?" These are the few moments Dark Souls has to make you feel this way and my gosh it almost gave me a roller coaster of feelings.
